     if the selected language is English:
    
     sec, second, seconds,
     min, minute, minutes,
     hrs, hour, hours,
     day, days,
     week, weeks,
     month, months,
     year, years
    
     Note that it does not matter which form you use, 2 hour means
     the same as 2 hours (plural).
    
     Usage:
    
